projectThree

Class UnaryOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • projectThree.AbstractFunction
      • projectThree.UnaryOperation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Cos, Exp, Log, Sin

    public abstract class UnaryOperation
extends AbstractFunction
    An abstract class to group Unary Operations/Functions. These functions have one operator, with the following included: Log, Exp, Sin, Cos This abstract class declares needed behaviors Unary Functions.
    Version:
    CSDS132 - Spring 2024
    Author:
    Trevor Swan
